<h1 id="24-hipaa-mappings-to-onyx-controls">24. HIPAA Mappings to Onyx Controls</h1>

<p>Below is a list of HIPAA Safeguards and Requirements and the Onyx controls in place to meet those.</p>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th><strong>Administrative Controls</strong> HIPAA Rule</th>
<th>Onyx Control</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>Security Management Process - 164.308(a)(1)(i)</td>
<td>Risk Management Policy</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Assigned Security Responsibility - 164.308(a)(2)</td>
<td>Roles Policy</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Workforce Security - 164.308(a)(3)(i)</td>
<td>Employee Policies</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Information Access Management - 164.308(a)(4)(i)</td>
<td>System Access Policy</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Security Awareness and Training - 164.308(a)(5)(i)</td>
<td>Employee Policy</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Security Incident Procedures - 164.308(a)(6)(i)</td>
<td>IDS Policy</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Contingency Plan - 164.308(a)(7)(i)</td>
<td>Disaster Recovery Policy</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Evaluation - 164.308(a)(8)</td>
<td>Auditing Policy</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

